<subSubSection pageId="7" pageNumber="22" type="preliminary conservation status">
<paragraph pageId="7" pageNumber="22">Preliminary conservation status.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="7" pageNumber="22">
Critically Endangered (CR). In the field observation, less than 10 individuals were found along the trail to the summit of Mt. 
<normalizedToken originalValue="Rào">Rao</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken originalValue="Cô">Co</normalizedToken>
, in lower montane forest. The habitat is inside the protected areas of Vu Quang National Park, but based on criterion D of the IUCN Red List criteria (
<bibRefCitation author="IUCN" journalOrPublisher="Bioinformatics" pageId="8" pageNumber="23" refId="B17" refString="IUCN, 2012. IUCN Red List Categories and Criteria. Version 3.1. Second edition. IUCN Species Survival Commission, IUCN, Gland, Switzerland and Cambridge, UK." title="IUCN Red List Categories and Criteria. Version 3.1. Second edition. IUCN Species Survival Commission, IUCN, Gland, Switzerland and Cambridge, UK." year="2012">IUCN 2012</bibRefCitation>
), this species is qualified as CR. Further intensive inventories are needed to find additional populations in Vu Quang National Park and its surrounding areas.
</paragraph>
